N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 332.4 - Entry in register of voters

State Regulations

All data contained in an application received by the boards
of elections from the division shall be entered in the register of voters
and/or on the registration records of the appropriate election
district. Notes
